7 SECTION 2. EXTRA HELP - SHARED SERVICES. There is hereby authorized,
8 for the Department of Agriculture - Shared Services for the 2025-2026 fiscal
9 year, the following maximum number of part-time or temporary employees, to be
10 known as "Extra Help", payable from funds appropriated herein for such
11 purposes: three (3) temporary or part-time employees, when needed, at rates
12 of pay not to exceed those provided in the Uniform Classification and
13 Compensation Act, or its successor, or this act for the appropriate
14 classification.
15
