35 Determining the maximum number of employees and the maximum amount of
36 appropriation and general revenue funding for a state agency each fiscal year
32 03-31-2025 17:32:01 BSS012

As Engrossed: S1/29/25 S3/31/25 SB106
1 is the prerogative of the General Assembly. This is usually accomplished by
2 delineating such maximums in the appropriation act(s) for a state agency and
3 the general revenue allocations authorized for each fund and fund account by
4 amendment to the Revenue Stabilization law. Further, the General Assembly
5 has determined that the Arkansas Agriculture Department - Livestock and
6 Poultry Commission may operate more efficiently if some flexibility is
7 provided to the Arkansas Agriculture Department - Livestock and Poultry
8 Commission authorizing broad powers under this Section. Therefore, it is
9 both necessary and appropriate that the General Assembly maintain oversight
