19 dollars ($1,180,100) of the amount authorized for transfer by Act 154 of
20 2012, to the State Forestry Fund.
21 (2) The transfer authority provided to the department in subdivision (A)(1)
22 of this section may be used in furtherance of the State Forestry Trust
23 Program.
24 (3) The provisions of this section shall be in effect only from July 1, 2025
25 through June 30, 2026.
