17 report to the Arkansas Legislative Council all amounts carried forward by the
18 September Arkansas Legislative Council or Joint Budget Committee meeting
19 which report shall include the name of the Agency, Board, Commission or
20 Institution and the amount of the funding carried forward from the first
21 fiscal year to the second fiscal year, the program name or line item, the
22 funding source of that appropriation and a copy of the written request set
23 forth in (1) above;
