25 report to the Arkansas Legislative Council or Joint Budget Committee
26 containing all information set forth in item (2) above, along with a written
27 statement as to the current status of the project, contract, purpose etc. for
28 which the carry forward was originally requested no later than thirty (30)
29 days prior to the time the Agency, Board, Commission or Institution presents
30 its budget request to the Arkansas Legislative Council/Joint Budget
31 Committee; and
32 (4) Thereupon, the Department of Finance and Administration shall include
33 all information obtained in item (3) above in the budget manuals and/or a
34 statement of non-compliance by the Agency, Board, Commission or Institution.
